wired into the latest sensory equipment, carrying state-of-the-art weaponry
– and late of the English Army''s Mindstar Battalion. As the cartels battle
for control of a revolutionary new power source, and corporate greed
outstrips national security, tension is mounting to boiling point – and
Greg Mandel is about to face the ultimate test.', '{"smallThumbnail": "http://books.google.com/books/content?id=1G6iuAAACAAJ&printsec=frontcover&img=1&zoom=5&source=gbs_api", "thumbnail": "http://books.google.com/books/content?id=1G6iuAAACAAJ&printsec=frontcover&img=1&zoom=1&source=gbs_api"}', '2011-01-01'::date, '["Peter F. Hamilton"]');
