aboard a damaged ship, on a seventeen-month gauntlet to reach the colony of
Hope Nation. With no chance of rescue or reinforcement, Nicholas Seafort
must overcome despair, exhaustion and guilt. He must conquer malfunctions,
mutiny and an alien horror beyond human understanding. And he must save
lives, and take them - in the name of duty.', '{"smallThumbnail": "http://books.google.com/books/content?id=rcw0HQAACAAJ&printsec=frontcover&img=1&zoom=5&source=gbs_api", "thumbnail": "http://books.google.com/books/content?id=rcw0HQAACAAJ&printsec=frontcover&img=1&zoom=1&source=gbs_api"}', '1996-01-01'::date, '["David Feintuch"]');
